{"tid":2171560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生存的意義","createTime":"2020-08-24T04:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T05:06:49.000Z","uid":367758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16034daaeaf7db749807accdb189e9ef706d7277","tid":2171560,"uid":367758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"就係冇意義"},{"pid":"eac88de4730c0f26a17a129d32ce2df6ffb6ac81","tid":2171560,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:40:32.000Z","msg":"『孤寂，是存在的本質。<br />\n　<br />\n任何一個人的「心」，都是52赫茲的深海鯨魚。<br />\n　<br />\n你出生的時候一個人來，你走的時候一個人去，<br />\n只有中間一段因為各種製造出來的忙碌，<br />\n遮住你的「初眼」，使你暫時忘記「存在」這回事。<br />\n　<br />\n我們中間這段路，都是對生命初衷的暫時失智。』<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;龍應台"},{"pid":"a55311f696428045eebb22f2298798edfee47eb5","tid":2171560,"uid":282872,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:58:15.000Z","msg":"就係搵出真正嘅意義"},{"pid":"8a1badb3c61108ef7a89331674b6b88d2a23d848","tid":2171560,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:05:10.000Z","msg":"死？"},{"pid":"864f41734ed3a6bfc0f6ffbb6e17ab31e9489144","tid":2171560,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:06:49.000Z","msg":"上帝早已預備"}]}